'''2018年國家聯盟中區封王決勝加賽'''[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]{{mlby|2018}}賽季的一場{{le|決勝加賽|one-game playoff}}，目的是從{{le|2018年密爾瓦基釀酒人隊球季|2018 Milwaukee Brewers season|密爾瓦基釀酒人隊}}和{{le|2018年芝加哥小熊隊隊球季|2018 Chicago Cubs season|芝加哥小熊隊}}中決定誰在[[國家聯盟|國家聯盟]][[國家聯盟中區|中區]]封王。這場比賽舉行於2018年10月1日[[伊利諾州|伊利諾州]][[芝加哥|芝加哥]]的[[瑞格利球場|瑞格利球場]]。

釀酒人隊最終以3比1取勝，並以第一種子序位晉級國聯季後賽。小熊隊則是在10月2日的[[2018年國家聯盟外卡晉級賽|外卡晉級賽]]中，以主場身分迎戰[[2018年國家聯盟西區封王決勝加賽|國聯西區第二]]的{{le|2018年科羅拉多落磯隊球季|2018 Colorado Rockies season|科羅拉多落磯隊}}。最終落磯隊擊敗小熊隊晉級[[2018年國家聯盟分區賽|2018年國家聯盟分區賽]]來面對釀酒人隊<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2018/09/30/mlb-playoffs-tiebreakers-dodgers-rockies-cubs-brewers/1481842002/|title=Game 163! Historic day on tap as Dodgers-Rockies, Cubs-Brewers set for NL tiebreakers Monday|last=Lacques|first=Greg|work=USA Today|date=2018-09-30|access-date=2018-09-30|archive-date=2020-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201222111647/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2018/09/30/mlb-playoffs-tiebreakers-dodgers-rockies-cubs-brewers/1481842002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

這場決勝加賽將被視為兩隊正規賽季的第163場比賽，比賽中的各項數據與內容也會算入正規賽季的統計當中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24853543/mlb-breaking-monday-division-tiebreaker-doubleheader |title=MLB - Breaking down Monday's division tiebreaker doubleheader |work=ESPN |date=2018-10-01 |access-date=2018-11-26 |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109154752/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24853543/mlb-breaking-monday-division-tiebreaker-doubleheader |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==背景==
{{main|{{le|2018年密爾瓦基釀酒人隊球季|2018 Milwaukee Brewers season}}|{{le|2018年芝加哥小熊隊隊球季|2018 Chicago Cubs season}}}}
[[芝加哥小熊隊|芝加哥小熊隊]]在[[2018年美國職棒大聯盟球季|2018年美國職棒大聯盟球季]]以前已連續兩年在[[國家聯盟中區|國家聯盟中區]]封王<ref>{{cite web |last=Neveau |first=James |url=https://www.nbcchicago.com/news/local/chicago-cubs-clinching-scenarios-saturday-national-league-central-magic-number-milwaukee-brewers-494696781.html |title=Chicago Cubs Clinching Scenarios: Saturday |publisher=NBC Chicago |date=2018-09-22 |access-date=2018-10-02 |archive-date=2018-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002064903/https://www.nbcchicago.com/news/local/chicago-cubs-clinching-scenarios-saturday-national-league-central-magic-number-milwaukee-brewers-494696781.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而[[密爾瓦基釀酒人隊|密爾瓦基釀酒人隊]]則是自2011年以來首度晉級[[美國職棒大聯盟季後賽|美國職棒大聯盟季後賽]]，當時他們也曾在中區封王過<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.jsonline.com/story/sports/mlb/brewers/2018/09/26/brewers-2-cardinals-1-first-playoff-berth-since-2011-assured/1426167002/ |title=Brewers 2, Cardinals 1: First playoff berth since 2011 is assured |publisher=Jsonline.com |access-date=2018-10-02 |archive-date=2020-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200224192046/https://www.jsonline.com/story/sports/mlb/brewers/2018/09/26/brewers-2-cardinals-1-first-playoff-berth-since-2011-assured/1426167002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

小熊隊和釀酒人隊在2018年正規賽季結束時以{{winning percentage|95|67|record=y}}的勝率並列分區第一<ref>{{cite web |last=McCalvy |first=Adam |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/brewers-set-for-game-163-against-cubs/c-296667402 |title=Brewers set for Game 163 against Cubs |publisher=MLB.com |date=2018-05-24 |access-date=2018-10-01 |archive-date=2018-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181001142359/https://www.mlb.com/news/brewers-set-for-game-163-against-cubs/c-296667402 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而釀酒人隊曾在季末拉出一波八[[連勝_(運動)|連勝]]<ref name=jsonline/>。由於[[洛杉磯道奇隊|洛杉磯道奇隊]]和[[科羅拉多落磯隊|科羅拉多落磯隊]]也並列[[國家聯盟西區|國家聯盟西區]]第一，因此他們也打了一場[[2018年國家聯盟西區封王決勝加賽|決勝加賽]]，這意味著[[美國職棒大聯盟|大聯盟]]將進行史上第一次的單年兩場決勝加賽<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24853543/mlb-breaking-monday-division-tiebreaker-doubleheader |title=MLB - Breaking down Monday's division tiebreaker doubleheader |publisher=Espn.com |access-date=2018-10-02 |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109154752/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24853543/mlb-breaking-monday-division-tiebreaker-doubleheader |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於釀酒人隊和小熊隊在國聯也是並列第一，因此不論他們哪隊落敗，都還是能打[[2018年國家聯盟外卡晉級賽|隔天的外卡晉級賽]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Snyder |first=Matt |url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/brewers-vs-cubs-in-nl-central-tiebreaker-what-to-know-about-pivotal-game-163-in-chicago/ |title=Brewers vs. Cubs in NL Central tiebreaker: What to know about pivotal Game 163 in Chicago |publisher=CBSSports.com |date=2018-10-01 |access-date=2018-11-26 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109012156/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/brewers-vs-cubs-in-nl-central-tiebreaker-what-to-know-about-pivotal-game-163-in-chicago/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

