小熊隊因為在正規賽季對戰釀酒人隊的成績較佳，因此他們取得這場比賽的[[主場優勢|主場優勢]]。小熊隊的先發投手派出[[荷西·昆塔納|荷西·昆塔納]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Muskat |first=Carrie |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/cubs-top-cardinals-face-brewers-in-tiebreaker/c-296662782 |title=Cubs top Cardinals, face Brewers in tiebreaker |publisher=MLB.com |date=2018-05-24 |access-date=2018-10-01 |archive-date=2018-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181001070333/https://www.mlb.com/news/cubs-top-cardinals-face-brewers-in-tiebreaker/c-296662782 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，釀酒人隊則推出{{le|朱利斯·查欣|Jhoulys Chacín}}先發<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24858900/jhoulys-chacin-start-brewers-tiebreaker-decide-nl-central |title=Jhoulys Chacin to start for Brewers in tiebreaker to decide NL Central |publisher=Espn.com |access-date=2018-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129045928/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24858900/jhoulys-chacin-start-brewers-tiebreaker-decide-nl-central |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這場比賽的電視轉播是由[[ESPN|ESPN]]負責，播報員包括{{le|卡爾·拉維奇|Karl Ravech}}、{{le|愛德華多·佩雷斯|Eduardo Pérez}}、{{le|提姆·科爾真安|Tim Kurkjian}}和{{le|巴斯特·奧爾尼|Buster Olney}}。此外，廣播轉播也由[[ESPN廣播|ESPN廣播]]負責，播報員有{{le|傑森·貝內蒂|Jason Benetti}}和{{le|克里斯·辛格萊頓 (棒球選手)|Chris Singleton (baseball)|克里斯·辛格萊頓}}<ref>{{cite web |last=Cafardo |first=Ben |url=https://espnmediazone.com/us/press-releases/2018/09/espn-to-exclusively-televise-both-mlb-national-league-tiebreaker-games-on-monday/ |title=ESPN To Exclusively Televise Both MLB National League Tiebreaker Games On Monday - ESPN MediaZone U.S |publisher=Espnmediazone.com |date=2018-09-30 |access-date=2018-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002214909/https://espnmediazone.com/us/press-releases/2018/09/espn-to-exclusively-televise-both-mlb-national-league-tiebreaker-games-on-monday/ |archive-date=2018-10-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.hudsonvalley.com/hudson-valley-sports-tv/2018/09/30/espn-espn-radio-have-coverage-of-mondays-baseball-playoffs/ |title=ESPN, ESPN Radio have coverage of Monday’s baseball playoffs |publisher=Blogs.hudsonvalley.com |date=2018-09-30 |access-date=2018-10-07 |archive-date=2021-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108235341/http://blogs.hudsonvalley.com/hudson-valley-sports-tv/2018/09/30/espn-espn-radio-have-coverage-of-mondays-baseball-playoffs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[克里斯蒂安·葉力奇|克里斯蒂安·葉力奇]]在三局上半打出一支一分[[打點|打點]][[一壘安打|一壘安打]]，釀酒人隊先馳得點。小熊隊則在五局下半反攻，靠著[[安東尼·瑞佐|安東尼·瑞佐]]的陽春[[全壘打|全壘打]]追平比數<ref name=tribune>{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-spt-cubs-brewers-20181001-story.html |title=Cold bats cost the Cubs in NL Central tiebreaker loss to the Brewers |publisher=Chicago Tribune |date=2018-08-30 |access-date=2018-10-02 |archive-date=2019-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190406082900/https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-spt-cubs-brewers-20181001-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雙方平手來到八局上半，釀酒人隊的[[洛倫佐·肯恩|洛倫佐·肯恩]]和[[萊恩·布勞恩|萊恩·布勞恩]]接連擊出帶有一分打點一壘安打，釀酒人隊取得3比1領先<ref name=gamesummary>{{cite web |title=Milwaukee Brewers at Chicago Cubs Box Score, October 1, 2018 |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHN/CHN201810010.shtml |work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]] |accessdate=2021-01-06 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116161047/https://www.baseball-reference.com/boxes/CHN/CHN201810010.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最後釀酒人隊靠著[[賈許·海德|賈許·海德]]在九局下半守成，拿下勝利<ref name=gamesummary/>。[[奧蘭多·阿西亞|奧蘭多·阿西亞]]首度單場四安，還成功跑回兩分<ref>{{cite web |author=R.J. Anderson |url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/brewers-vs-cubs-final-score-things-to-know-milwaukee-wins-nl-central-in-tiebreaker-game/ |title=Brewers vs. Cubs final score, things to know: Milwaukee wins NL Central in tiebreaker game |publisher=CBSSports.com |access-date=2018-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128201501/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/brewers-vs-cubs-final-score-things-to-know-milwaukee-wins-nl-central-in-tiebreaker-game/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==後續==
釀酒人隊取勝後，成功在國聯及西區登頂，隨後在[[2018年國家聯盟分區賽|國聯分區賽]]中以3比0橫掃[[科羅拉多落磯隊|科羅拉多落磯隊]]，晉級[[2018年國家聯盟冠軍賽|2018年國家聯盟冠軍賽]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2018/10/07/brewers-rockies-sweep-craig-counsell-mlb-playoffs/1561904002/ |title=MLB playoffs: Brewers punch NLCS ticket with savvy moves, platoon help |publisher=Usatoday.com |access-date=2018-11-26 |archive-date=2020-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001020546/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2018/10/07/brewers-rockies-sweep-craig-counsell-mlb-playoffs/1561904002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但他們在國聯冠軍賽上與[[洛杉磯道奇隊|洛杉磯道奇隊]]力戰七場後敗陣<ref name=jsonline>{{cite web |url=https://www.jsonline.com/story/sports/mlb/brewers/2018/10/01/brewers-3-cubs-1-milwaukee-wins-nl-central-title-wrigley-field/1483649002/ |title=Brewers 3, Cubs 1: Milwaukee wins NL Central title at Wrigley Field |publisher=Jsonline.com |access-date=2018-10-02 |archive-date=2020-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025171646/https://www.jsonline.com/story/sports/mlb/brewers/2018/10/01/brewers-3-cubs-1-milwaukee-wins-nl-central-title-wrigley-field/1483649002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

小熊隊這場輸球後，以外卡第一之姿結束賽季。隔天的[[2018年國家聯盟外卡晉級賽|外卡晉級賽]]中，他們以主場身分迎戰[[2018年國家聯盟西區封王決勝加賽|國聯西區第二]]的{{le|2018年科羅拉多落磯隊球季|2018 Colorado Rockies season|科羅拉多落磯隊}}，但在延長賽鏖戰13局後敗北<ref name=tribune/>。

